OL,3,CTimothee Chalamet criticised for
OL,4,Csaying 'no one cares' about opera and
OL,5,Cballet
OL,7,FOscar-nominated actor Timothee
OL,8,FChalamet has faced backlash on social
OL,9,Fmedia after saying he does not want to
OL,10,Fwork in opera or ballet as "no one
OL,11,Fcares" about them.
OL,13,FThe Marty Supreme star made the
OL,14,Fremarks to fellow actor Matthew
OL,15,FMcConaughey in an interview for US
OL,16,Foutlet Variety about the future of
OL,17,Fcinema.
OL,26,@kD@GrroD@]rr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
