OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772986287
OL,3,CTimothee Chalamet criticised for
OL,4,Csaying 'no one cares' about opera and
OL,5,Cballet
OL,7,F"I don't want to be working in ballet
OL,8,For opera or, you know, things where
OL,9,Fit's like, 'hey, keep this thing
OL,10,Falive', even though no one cares about
OL,11,Fthis anymore," he said.
OL,13,F"All respect to the ballet and opera
OL,14,Fpeople out there", he quickly added.
OL,15,F"I just lost 14 cents in viewership. I
OL,16,Fjust took shots for no reason."
OL,18,FMcConaughey added: "That's not a shot,
OL,19,FI hear what you're saying."
OL,26,@kD@GrrzD@TOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
