PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772986287
OL,3,CTimothee Chalamet criticised for
OL,4,Csaying 'no one cares' about opera and
OL,5,Cballet
OL,7,FThe comments have drawn criticism from
OL,8,Fthe performing arts world, including
OL,9,FUS opera singer Isabel Leonard,
OL,10,FHollywood star Jamie Lee Curtis and
OL,11,FCanadian mezzo-soprano Deepa Johnny.
OL,13,FLeonard said in a comment on the video
OL,14,Fposted to Variety's Instagram:
OL,15,F"Honestly, I'm shocked that someone so
OL,16,Fseemingly successful can be so
OL,17,Fineloquent and narrow minded in his
OL,18,Fviews about art while considering
OL,19,Fhimself as artist as I would only
OL,20,Fimagine one would as an actor.
OL,26,@kD@GrrwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772986287
OL,3,CTimothee Chalamet criticised for
OL,4,Csaying 'no one cares' about opera and
OL,5,Cballet
OL,7,F"To take cheap shots at fellow artists
OL,8,Fsays more in this interview than
OL,9,Fanything else he could say. Shows a
OL,10,Flot about his character.
OL,12,F"You don't have to like all art but
OL,13,Fonly a weak person/artist feels the
OL,14,Fneed to diminish in fact the very arts
OL,15,Fthat would inspire those who are
OL,16,Finterested in slowing down, to do
OL,17,Fexactly that."
OL,26,@kD@GrroD@AOUtD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
