OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FJohnny added in another comment: "What
OL,13,Fa disappointing take. There is nothing
OL,14,Fmore impressive than the magic of live
OL,15,Ftheatre, ballet and opera.
OL,17,F"We should be trying to uplift these
OL,18,Fart forms, these artists and come
OL,19,Ftogether across disciplines to do
OL,20,Fthat. The impact of these mediums are
OL,21,Flong lasting and life-changing."
OL,26,@kD@GrrtD@bOUyD@AOU}D@`O]
