OL,3,CTimothee Chalamet criticised for
OL,4,Csaying 'no one cares' about opera and
OL,5,Cballet
OL,7,FWhile Jamie Lee Curtis asked in an
OL,8,FInstagram Story: "Why are any artists
OL,9,Ftaking shots at any other artists?"
OL,11,FThe English National Ballet also took
OL,12,Fto Instagram to address the actor's
OL,13,Fcomments, writing: "We're happy to
OL,14,Freport that ballet is not only alive
OL,15,Fand well, but thriving."
OL,17,FIts post continued: "Over 200,000
OL,18,Fpeople joined our performances,
OL,19,Fexperiencing the power of ballet.
OL,26,@kD@Grr
