OL,7,F"Our social content saw over 65m
OL,8,Fimpressions and we connected with
OL,9,Fthousands of people of all ages and
OL,10,Fwalks of life through creative
OL,11,Flearning and participation."
OL,13,FChalamet has been contacted by the PA
OL,14,FNews agency for comment.
